name: Photography
tagline: A repository for photos from photography
body:
This website aims to display shots taken over the last few weeks and months that either illustrate constructs or concepts 
from photography, or exist as individual projects.

The following links will bring you to other parts of the site. This is the current home page.
Above can be found downloads for the various images used (eventually).

[**The official page for snapshots**](http://danforthphoto.github.io/snapshots/)

[**The official page for before and after shots**](http://danforthphoto.github.io/beforeandafter/)

[**The official page for billboard images**](http://danforthphoto.github.io/billboard/)
